{"article_id":"vTgwwh617iKkF0na","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Tuesday night , in his fifth State of the Union address , Mr. Obama will lay out a familiar litany of goals .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"He wants to reduce income inequality ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"boost opportunity ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and reform the immigration system .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"He will highlight the coming end of US military involvement in Afghanistan .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"He will talk climate change .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"He will defend his health-care reform .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"And in a move","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"to spur Congress to act on income inequality ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Obama will announce a plan","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"to raise the minimum wage for workers on new federal government contracts to $ 10.10 per hour ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"according to The Washington Post .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"He will do so via an executive order ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"following his pledge","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to use his executive powers","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to advance his agenda .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"But almost as important as what he says","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"will be how he says it .","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"By the end of 2013 , Obama was sounding weary , even a little defeated , after a year of stumbles","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"- on gun control , on Syria , on Obamacare .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Now , Obama ' s job approval ratings are ticking upward","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"( though still below 50 percent ) ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and he has a new mantra :","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"He ' s ready to use \" the pen and the phone \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to move his agenda forward .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"That ' s his way","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"of saying ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"\" Watch out , Congress .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"If you don ' t give me what I want ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"I ' m going to use my executive powers","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"to act on my own . \"","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"2014 will be a \" year of action , \"","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Team Obama says .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"And there ' s nothing like giving an address to a joint session of Congress ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"televised live to the nation","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"( and the globe ) ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"to get the presidential juices going .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Some 30 million people are expected to watch .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"you ' ll see him feeling energized tomorrow , \"","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"says Peter Fenn , a Democratic strategist .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"\" As much as he is cool , calm , and collected ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and as much as he sees and plays the long game ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"he ' s not averse to going to the basket .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"He ' ll be in take-charge mode . \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"But what happens the next day ?","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"Literally , Obama gets on Air Force One","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"and flies around the country","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to give more speeches .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"And he will , once again , have to fight to be heard above the din of politics - the already fierce media obsession with the 2016 presidential race and , increasingly , the November midterms ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"which will determine","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"whether the Republicans retake the Senate for Obama ' s final two years in office .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Still , on Tuesday night , the stage will be Obama ' s - his best chance","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to set the agenda for the remainder of his presidency ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"even if it ' s just a reassertion of agendas past .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"\" It ' s difficult for presidents in their last years to initiate new proposals","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and have the Congress take him seriously , \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"says Cal Jillson , a political scientist at Southern Methodist University in Dallas .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"\" But presidents remain consequential .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"It ' s always true that being president of the United States means you have your hands on the levers of power . \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Even if Obama ' s impasse with Congress holds ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"the president will still face the inevitable emergencies and foreign policy challenges .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Speaking on talk shows Sunday ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"top Obama aides laid down the gauntlet to Congress .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"\" What we saw last year in 2013 was a Washington","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that did not deliver for the American people , \"","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"White House press secretary Jay Carney said on ABC 's `` This Week . ''","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"\" The president sees this as a year of action ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"to work with Congress","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"where he can","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and to bypass Congress","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"where necessary .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"To lift folks","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"who want to come up into the middle class . \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Senior adviser Dan Pfeiffer echoed those remarks on Fox News Sunday :","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"what you 're going to hear from the president on Tuesday night is a series of concrete , practical , specific proposals","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"on how we restore opportunity , through a wide set of means","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"- job training , education , manufacturing , energy .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"There will be some legislative proposals ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"but also a number of actions","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"he can take on his own .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" The one significant area","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"where there is potential for progress this year","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"is immigration reform .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Congressional Republicans are prepared to move forward with piecemeal legislation , instead of a comprehensive package .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Obama has said","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"he ' s willing to go along with smaller bills ,","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"as long as a path to citizenship is in the mix .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"Republicans know","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"to make progress with Hispanic voters ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"they need to move on immigration .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"The question is when .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"The issue matters in a handful of congressional districts , and some key statewide races this November ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"but immigration is a more critical issue for the presidential race in 2016 .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"The GOP ' s nominee in 2012 , Mitt Romney , got only 27 percent of the Hispanic vote .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Republicans must do better with this fast-growing demographic","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"if they ever hope to retake the White House .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"If Republicans move on immigration reform this year ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that ' s when Obama ' s promise/threat of executive action comes into play .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"The GOP can move on some small initiatives ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"such as codifying into law the Obama administration ' s move in 2012","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"to delay deportation of young illegal immigrants .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"It could also move to create a new guest worker program .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":109,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":110,"text":"\" This is where Obama really has the opportunity","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"to use his pen and his phone more quickly","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"than the Republican majority of the House can act , \"","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"says Mr. Jillson .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"\" When the Republican majority looks like it ' s about to do something interesting ,","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"he can get ahead of them with an administrative initiative on immigration ,","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"as he ' s done in the past . \"","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"The question will be whether that ' s smart politics .","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"Republicans would likely be furious","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"if the president scooped them again on an immigration initiative .","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"given the cool relationship between Obama and Republican leaders on Capitol Hill ,","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"maybe that wouldn ' t matter .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":245,"left":227,"right":244,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":227,"left":140,"right":226,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":140,"left":138,"right":139,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":0,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":125,"right":136,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":1,"right":124,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":127,"right":135,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left